OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fshowers becoming widespread this
OL,7,Fevening, likely merging into more
OL,8,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy rain
OL,9,Fovernight. Rain only erratically
OL,10,Fclearing northeast after dawn, but
OL,11,Fstill some locally heavy showers
OL,12,Ffollowing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FEarly cloud will break with
OL,15,Fsome bright or sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping, but also scattered
OL,17,Fshowers. These turning heavy in
OL,18,Fplaces, with thunder and hail
OL,19,Fpossible, especially during the
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
